Displays HeaderItems on the right side of the Fiori launchpad shell header, in the given launchpad states (see sap.ushell.renderers.fiori2.Renderer.LaunchpadState).</br> If no launchpad state is provided the content is displayed in all states.</br> The shell header can display the user HeaderItem, and just one more HeaderItem.</br> If this method is called when the right side of the header is full, this method will not do anything.</br>

