value='\{&quot;columns&quot;:\{&quot;visible&quot;: true, &quot;payload&quot;: \{&quot;visibleItemsThreshold&quot;: 3\}\}\}' /&gt;
/customData&gt;
</pre>

Default value is <code>-1</code>.

